snippet: Ayako Uehara of Japan took the lead Thursday at the Women’s British Open in Southport, England, with a four-under-par 68, not making a bogey after the opening hole.
abstract: Ayako Uehara of Japan takes first-round lead at the Women’s British Open in Southport, England; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Ayako Uehara of Japan took the lead Thursday at the Women’s British Open in Southport, England, with a four-under-par 68, not making a bogey after the opening hole.
